{
  "text": "Several workers have reported that darker shades and increased opacity were found to cause energy attenuation and diminished light through transmission [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] which resulted in reduced curing of the material [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "44612217",
